" ===== [ Copy to system clipboard (requires xsel) ] ================
autocmd Filetype    python
 \ nmap <leader>ca gg2jV/\nif __name__ == '__main__':<cr>cp<cr>
autocmd Filetype    cpp,c,cuda
 \ nmap <leader>ca gg2jV/\n\nint main <cr>cp<cr>
